th, Suffrage, and Peace |date=1996 |publisher=Feminist Press |location=New York, New York |isbn=978-1-558-61138-2 |edition=English |url=https://archive.org/details/memoriesmylifeas00jaco/page/7}}\n*{{cite news |ref=harv |last1=Klotts |first1=Diana |title=She Predicted the World War: Rosika Schwimmer at Sixty (pt. 1) |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/38052797/the_wisconsin_jewish_chronicle/ |accessdate=28 October 2019 |agency=Seven Arts Feature Syndicate |date=10 December 1937 |newspaper=[[The Wisconsin Jewish Chronicle]] |location=Milwaukee, Wisconsin |page=1 |via=[[Newspapers.com]]}} and {{cite news |last1=Klotts |first1=Diana |title=She Predicted the World War (pt. 2) |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/38052858/the_wisconsin_jewish_chronicle/ |accessdate=28 October 2019 |agency=Seven Arts Feature Syndicate |date=10 December 1937 |newspaper=[[The Wisconsin Jewish Chronicle]] |location=Milwaukee, Wisconsin |page=9 |via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}\n*{{cite news |ref=harv |last1=Marshall |first1=Margaret Mooers |title=Bitter War of the Sexes Will Follow Europe's War; A Struggle for 'The Job' |url=https://www.newspapers.com/clip/38036972/daily_arkansas_gazette/ |accessdate=28 October 2019 |date=4 September 1916 |newspaper=[[Arkansas Gazette]] |location=Little Rock, Arkansas |page=5 |via=[[Newspapers.com]]}}\n*{{cite book |ref=harv |last=Nielsen |first=Kim E. |title=Un-American Womanhood: Antiradicalism, Antifeminism, and the First Red Scare |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=evShjdEUXygC&pg=PA79 |date=2001 |publisher=[[Ohio State University Press]] |location=Columbus, Ohio|isbn=978-0-8142-0882-3}}\n*{{cite web |ref=harv |last1=Ny\u00e1ry |first1=Kriszti\u00e1n |title=A magyar feminista, akit Nobel-b\u00e9ked\u00edjra is jel\u00f6ltek |url=https://index.hu/tudomany/tortenelem/2017/07/01/a_magyar_feminista_akit_nobel-bekedijra_is_jeloltek/ |website=[[Index (Hungarian website)|Index]] |publisher=[[BBC History]] |accessdate=26 October 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive